Located in Ikeja, a 11-minute walk from Kalakuta Museum, Ivy Hotel Ikeja Lagos provides accommodations with a shared lounge, free private parking, a restaurant and a bar. This 4-star hotel offers a concierge service and a tour desk. The property has room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests.

A buffet, continental or Full English/Irish breakfast is served at the property.

National Stadium Lagos is 16.1 km from the hotel, while Synagogue Church Of all Nations is 17.7 km away. The nearest airport is Murtala Muhammed International Airport, 4 km from Ivy Hotel Ikeja Lagos.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 8.4 for a two-person trip.

Ivy Hotel Ikeja Lagos has been welcoming Booking.com guests since Feb 3, 2022
